strings.Value: "I can't believe that none of you see how unnatural Tristian's behavior is! No one is a saint. — He's obviously holding something back!"
"Why, you can't believe that everyone else isn't as self-centered as you?"
"Ha, like Harrim is anywhere close to normal. We're quite a circus. — Clowns, freaks, and magicians."
"I doubt the snotnose could hide anything from me."
